Source: boost-mongo
Maintainer: Sebastian Jeltsch <sjeltsch@kip.uni-heidelberg.de>
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8)
Homepage: https://github.com/ignatz/boost_mongo.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/ignatz/boost_mongo.git

Package: libboost-mongo0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB and JSON boost::serialization archive
 The library provides a boost::serialization conforming library to store and
 load data from your mongo database. Furthermore, serialization from and to JSON
 is provided by means of the mongodb C++ client drivers.
